{"tid":1010082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"tag酒鬼衝一波！全球首間「啤酒旅館」開幕　打開水龍頭就能暢飲","createTime":"2019-02-05T16:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T17:25:38.000Z","uid":212399,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"148f316e13d378d27516f2452a71f065ce6a96dc","tid":1010082,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T16:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3878/d3878679.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3878%2Fd3878679.jpg&h=677f6778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文／班尼<br />\n還記得2018年2月底時，蘇格蘭啤酒品牌Brewdog宣布要開設名為「DogHouse」的啤酒旅館嗎？標榜「打開水龍頭就能暢飲」引起全世界酒鬼們拍手叫好，而現在美國俄亥俄州的分店先行開幕，等不及的人們快衝一波～<br />\n跟預計開在阿伯丁郡（Aberdeen）的啤酒旅館一樣，俄亥俄州的32間客房中，每天早晨都會被啤酒香氣「香醒」，是許多人最夢寐以求的起床方式。許多房間還能俯瞰啤酒廠、欣賞工人的工作實況。<br />\n最吸睛的，莫過於每個房間都備有「啤酒水龍頭」，隨時打開都有取之不盡的生啤酒。浴室也內置啤酒冰箱，一邊淋浴時，能使用啤酒花香皂，再一邊享受美酒，人生就該如此美好！<br />\n而針對想了解釀酒知識的人，也是一大天堂！除了有相關書籍，也設有互動啤酒博物館，能深入了解啤酒的生產過程。從官網上顯示，一晚從162美金（約4984元）起，另有其他兩種更高級的房型可選擇，甚至可以帶狗狗入住，酒鬼們快列入人生清單吧！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3878/d3878682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3878%2Fd3878682.jpg&h=e5acb4ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3878/d3878680.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3878%2Fd3878680.jpg&h=a789b382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://fashion.ettoday.net/news/1371514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffashion.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1371514&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=cda9becf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fashion.ettoday.net/news/1371514</a>"},{"pid":"742c6503a9d82be8e18f6b7d2d21dcf8a30edddc","tid":1010082,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T16:35:30.000Z","msg":"幾時有糖果旅館<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成間旅館都食得"},{"pid":"1d3f9bb2b37fd2cdfd9a0ae319c6ac4be32c390c","tid":1010082,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T16:35:55.000Z","msg":"啤酒沖涼ok？一路沖一路奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdedac24110b6dce7f84051ea21f28bc1623b3e","tid":1010082,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T16:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b8045fbb5365d14e5f53cea2d36e3cd6ffc03e","tid":1010082,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"甲由都好鍾意啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2a38c04a2f4f0ec9e5231e398586fa0a194ec9","tid":1010082,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T17:25:38.000Z","msg":"衝你老母一波"}]}